lead_paragraph: FIFA presidential candidate Prince Ali Bin Al Hussein of Jordan's request for Friday's election to be postponed because of an issue with the voting booths has been rejected by sport's highest tribunal

headline.print_headline: Prince Ali Loses Appeal Asking for FIFA Election to Be Suspended
